text: "Lead Me On" is a 1971 song by country singers Loretta Lynn and Conway Twitty. It is the title track from their album Lead Me On and the country single charts in the United States and Canada. ==References== Category:1971 songs Category:Loretta Lynn songs Category:Conway Twitty songs Category:Country songs
title: Lead Me On (Loretta Lynn and Conway Twitty song)
